  "link": "http://www.cnbeta.com/articles/241932.htm", 
  "description": "<p>人类大脑的内部工作原理，仍然是一个相当神秘的前沿课题。尽管我们已经学习了几十年，但最近完成的一项工作，应该能够提供前所未有的内部细节。<strong>据《自然》报道，科学家们已经成功地绘制出了人类大脑的完整3D地图。</strong>这个艰难的过程，涉及到将一名65岁女性的大脑切成7400片，每一片比人的头发丝还细。</p><img border=\"0\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://cnbeta.feedsportal.com/c/34306/f/624776/s/2d9448c1/mf.gif\" width=\"1\" /><div class=\"mf-viral\"><table border=\"0\"><tr><td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/twitter/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F241932.htm&amp;t=%E7%A7%91%E5%AD%A6%E5%AE%B6%E6%88%90%E5%8A%9F%E7%BB%98%E5%88%B6%E4%BA%BA%E7%B1%BB%E5%A4%A7%E8%84%913D%E5%9B%BE+%E7%B2%BE%E5%BA%A650%E5%80%8D%E4%BA%8E%E4%BB%A5%E5%BE%80\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/twitter.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/facebook/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F241932.htm&amp;t=%E7%A7%91%E5%AD%A6%E5%AE%B6%E6%88%90%E5%8A%9F%E7%BB%98%E5%88%B6%E4%BA%BA%E7%B1%BB%E5%A4%A7%E8%84%913D%E5%9B%BE+%E7%B2%BE%E5%BA%A650%E5%80%8D%E4%BA%8E%E4%BB%A5%E5%BE%80\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/facebook.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/linkedin/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F241932.htm&amp;t=%E7%A7%91%E5%AD%A6%E5%AE%B6%E6%88%90%E5%8A%9F%E7%BB%98%E5%88%B6%E4%BA%BA%E7%B1%BB%E5%A4%A7%E8%84%913D%E5%9B%BE+%E7%B2%BE%E5%BA%A650%E5%80%8D%E4%BA%8E%E4%BB%A5%E5%BE%80\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/linkedin.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/gplus/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F241932.htm&amp;t=%E7%A7%91%E5%AD%A6%E5%AE%B6%E6%88%90%E5%8A%9F%E7%BB%98%E5%88%B6%E4%BA%BA%E7%B1%BB%E5%A4%A7%E8%84%913D%E5%9B%BE+%E7%B2%BE%E5%BA%A650%E5%80%8D%E4%BA%8E%E4%BB%A5%E5%BE%80\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/googleplus.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/email/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbe