  "description": "<p>微软继续假加强Surface品牌在教育市场的宣传力度，为学生教师提供非常诱人的折扣活动。<strong>今天微软WPC博客再次宣布参加下月召开的全球合作伙伴会议 （WPC）的与会者都能用$99的价格购买一台带Touch Cover的64GB的Surface RT，此外128GB的Surface Pro也能用$399.99的价格购买。</strong></p><img border=\"0\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://cnbeta.feedsportal.com/c/34306/f/624776/s/2d9448bf/mf.gif\" width=\"1\" /><div class=\"mf-viral\"><table border=\"0\"><tr><td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/twitter/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F241929.htm&amp;t=%E5%BE%AE%E8%BD%AF%E5%AE%A3%E5%B8%83WPC%E4%B8%8E%E4%BC%9A%E8%80%85%E5%8F%AF%2499%E8%B4%AD%E4%B9%B0Surface+RT\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/twitter.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/facebook/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F241929.htm&amp;t=%E5%BE%AE%E8%BD%AF%E5%AE%A3%E5%B8%83WPC%E4%B8%8E%E4%BC%9A%E8%80%85%E5%8F%AF%2499%E8%B4%AD%E4%B9%B0Surface+RT\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/facebook.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/linkedin/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F241929.htm&amp;t=%E5%BE%AE%E8%BD%AF%E5%AE%A3%E5%B8%83WPC%E4%B8%8E%E4%BC%9A%E8%80%85%E5%8F%AF%2499%E8%B4%AD%E4%B9%B0Surface+RT\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/linkedin.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/gplus/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F241929.htm&amp;t=%E5%BE%AE%E8%BD%AF%E5%AE%A3%E5%B8%83WPC%E4%B8%8E%E4%BC%9A%E8%80%85%E5%8F%AF%2499%E8%B4%AD%E4%B9%B0Surface+RT\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/googleplus.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/email/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F241929.htm&amp;t=%E5%BE%AE%E8%BD%AF%E5%AE%A3%E5%B8%83WPC%E4%B8%8E%E4%BC%9A%E8%80%85%E5%8F%AF%2499%E8%B4%AD%E4%B9%B0Surface+RT\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/s