  "date": "Fri, 21 Jun 2013 00:06:04 GMT", 
  "link": "http://www.cnbeta.com/articles/241931.htm", 
  "description": "<p><strong>美国专利商标局本周四公布了一项由苹果申请的感应器封装技术专利，该技术可以用更小巧，保护性更强的方式封装感应器和导电边框，从而使指纹感应器部件适用于移动设备。</strong>苹果于今年二月提交这项专利申请，专利名为“指纹感应器整体成型模具及边框结构”。该专利中描述的是一种单一封装结构，既可以保护脆弱的生物测量阵列，又允 许一部分感应器和导电边框能够暴露在外或者加封一层保护薄膜。这项专利申请针对的是“带状”的感应器，不过该技术也可以应用于其他指纹感应技术中。</p><p><br /></p><img border=\"0\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://cnbeta.feedsportal.com/c/34306/f/624776/s/2d9448be/mf.gif\" width=\"1\" /><div class=\"mf-viral\"><table border=\"0\"><tr><td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/twitter/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F241931.htm&amp;t=%E8%8B%B9%E6%9E%9C%E7%94%B3%E8%AF%B7%E6%8C%87%E7%BA%B9%E6%84%9F%E5%BA%94%E5%B0%81%E8%A3%85%E4%B8%93%E5%88%A9+%E6%9C%89%E6%9C%9B%E7%94%A8%E4%BA%8E%E6%9C%AA%E6%9D%A5iPhone\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/twitter.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/facebook/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F241931.htm&amp;t=%E8%8B%B9%E6%9E%9C%E7%94%B3%E8%AF%B7%E6%8C%87%E7%BA%B9%E6%84%9F%E5%BA%94%E5%B0%81%E8%A3%85%E4%B8%93%E5%88%A9+%E6%9C%89%E6%9C%9B%E7%94%A8%E4%BA%8E%E6%9C%AA%E6%9D%A5iPhone\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/facebook.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/linkedin/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F241931.htm&amp;t=%E8%8B%B9%E6%9E%9C%E7%94%B3%E8%AF%B7%E6%8C%87%E7%BA%B9%E6%84%9F%E5%BA%94%E5%B0%81%E8%A3%85%E4%B8%93%E5%88%A9+%E6%9C%89%E6%9C%9B%E7%94%A8%E4%BA%8E%E6%9C%AA%E6%9D%A5iPhone\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/linkedin.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/gplus/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F241931.htm&amp;t=%E8%8B%B9%E6%9E%9C%E7%94%B3%E8%AF%B7%E6%8C%87%E7%BA%B9%E6%84%9F%E5%BA%94%E5%B0%81%E8%A3%85%E4%B8%93%E5%88%A9+%E6%9C%89%E6%9C%9B%E7%94%A8%E4%BA%8E%E6%9C%AA%E6%9D%A5iPhone\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/goog