  "link": "http://www.cnbeta.com/articles/241927.htm", 
  "description": "<p> Facebook COO Sheryl Sandberg日前公开表示，他们对中国市场抱有巨大兴趣，仍在想法设法进入这里。Sheryl Sandberg强调，中国市场的潜力尚未得到挖掘，Facebook不会将这一市场拱手让给本地竞争对手。<strong>Sheryl Sandberg透露，Facebook目前正在与中国的相关部门进行谈判进入中国市场的事宜，但决定权并不在他们手中。</strong> </p> <p> <br /> </p><img border=\"0\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://cnbeta.feedsportal.com/c/34306/f/624776/s/2d9448ba/mf.gif\" width=\"1\" /><div class=\"mf-viral\"><table border=\"0\"><tr><td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/twitter/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F241927.htm&amp;t=Facebook%E4%B8%8D%E6%AD%BB%E5%BF%83+%E8%BF%98%E6%83%B3%E8%BF%9B%E5%85%A5%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/twitter.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/facebook/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F241927.htm&amp;t=Facebook%E4%B8%8D%E6%AD%BB%E5%BF%83+%E8%BF%98%E6%83%B3%E8%BF%9B%E5%85%A5%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/facebook.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/linkedin/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F241927.htm&amp;t=Facebook%E4%B8%8D%E6%AD%BB%E5%BF%83+%E8%BF%98%E6%83%B3%E8%BF%9B%E5%85%A5%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/linkedin.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/gplus/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F241927.htm&amp;t=Facebook%E4%B8%8D%E6%AD%BB%E5%BF%83+%E8%BF%98%E6%83%B3%E8%BF%9B%E5%85%A5%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/googleplus.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/email/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F241927.htm&amp;t=Facebook%E4%B8%8D%E6%AD%BB%E5%BF%83+%E8%BF%98%E6%83%B3%E8%BF%9B%E5%85%A5%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/email.png\" /></a></td><td valign=\"middle\