  "date": "Thu, 20 Jun 2013 23:43:55 GMT", 
  "link": "http://www.cnbeta.com/articles/241923.htm", 
  "description": "<p>美国北亚利桑那大学名誉教授科恩·斯洛博得契科夫是一名动物行为研究者，30年来他一直致力于研究破译动物语言，并将土拨鼠交流语言研究作为突破点。<strong>科恩认为，人类有望破译动物的语言，并利用计算机科技实现跟动物之间的交谈，人类将在5年到10年内发明能跟宠物交谈的设备。</strong></p><img border=\"0\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://cnbeta.feedsportal.com/c/34306/f/624776/s/2d9448b5/mf.gif\" width=\"1\" /><div class=\"mf-viral\"><table border=\"0\"><tr><td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/twitter/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F241923.htm&amp;t=%E5%80%9F%E5%8A%A9%E8%AE%A1%E7%AE%97%E6%9C%BA%E7%A7%91%E6%8A%80+10%E5%B9%B4%E5%90%8E%E4%BA%BA%E8%83%BD%E5%92%8C%E5%AE%A0%E7%89%A9%E2%80%9C%E8%81%8A%E5%A4%A9%E2%80%9D\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/twitter.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/facebook/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F241923.htm&amp;t=%E5%80%9F%E5%8A%A9%E8%AE%A1%E7%AE%97%E6%9C%BA%E7%A7%91%E6%8A%80+10%E5%B9%B4%E5%90%8E%E4%BA%BA%E8%83%BD%E5%92%8C%E5%AE%A0%E7%89%A9%E2%80%9C%E8%81%8A%E5%A4%A9%E2%80%9D\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/facebook.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/linkedin/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F241923.htm&amp;t=%E5%80%9F%E5%8A%A9%E8%AE%A1%E7%AE%97%E6%9C%BA%E7%A7%91%E6%8A%80+10%E5%B9%B4%E5%90%8E%E4%BA%BA%E8%83%BD%E5%92%8C%E5%AE%A0%E7%89%A9%E2%80%9C%E8%81%8A%E5%A4%A9%E2%80%9D\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/linkedin.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/gplus/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F241923.htm&amp;t=%E5%80%9F%E5%8A%A9%E8%AE%A1%E7%AE%97%E6%9C%BA%E7%A7%91%E6%8A%80+10%E5%B9%B4%E5%90%8E%E4%BA%BA%E8%83%BD%E5%92%8C%E5%AE%A0%E7%89%A9%E2%80%9C%E8%81%8A%E5%A4%A9%E2%80%9D\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/googleplus.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/email/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F2